@startuml diag_route_owner_to_gateway_open_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Diag Route Owner To Gateway Open Signal Flow\n(NAV/TMU route context -> SGW -> DCM / TEST_SCN)

participant "NAV / route context\nand boundary status" as RouteCtx #F4F7FB
participant "SGW\ndiagnostic gateway owner" as SGW #E8F7E8
participant "DCM\ndiagnostic response owner" as DCM #FFF4CC
participant "TEST_SCN\nverification observer" as TEST_SCN #FFE6E6

== Route / Boundary Inputs ==

RouteCtx -> SGW : routeActive / guidedRouteActive\nspeedLimit / vehicleSpeed\nCoreState::domainBoundaryStatus\nCoreState::warningPathStatus\nCore::failSafeMode
SGW -> SGW : ethHasBoundaryServiceContext()
SGW -> SGW : ethDiagBoundaryStage()
note right of SGW
Representative derived state
- gIboxRouteState
- gIboxServiceFlags
- securitySession
- authState
end note

== Diagnostic Gateway Ownership ==

SGW -> SGW : RouteOwner = 0/1/2
SGW -> SGW : GatewayOpen = routeActive
SGW -> SGW : SecurityState / AuthState / SecurityFault / SecurityPolicy
SGW -> DCM : Diag::RouteOwner\nDiag::GatewayOpen\nDiag::SecurityState
note right of SGW
Key diag seams
- Diag::RouteOwner
- Diag::GatewayOpen
- Diag::SecurityState
end note

== DCM Response Path ==

DCM -> DCM : derive ServiceState /\nResponseKind / ReasonCode
DCM -> DCM : publishDiagRequestObservation()
DCM -> DCM : publishDiagResponseObservation()
DCM -> TEST_SCN : Diag::ServiceState\nDiag::ResponseKind\nDiag::ReasonCode\nDiag::LastRequestSid\nDiag::LastResponseCode

== Verification / Evidence ==

TEST_SCN -> TEST_SCN : observe RouteOwner / GatewayOpen /\nServiceState / ReasonCode
TEST_SCN -> TEST_SCN : evaluate blocked or degraded\nservice context verdicts
note right of TEST_SCN
Representative checks
- RouteOwner == 1
- ServiceState == 2
- ResponseKind == 4
- ReasonCode == 2
end note

note over RouteCtx, TEST_SCN
Representative runtime chain
1. Route/boundary context reaches SGW
2. SGW owns RouteOwner and GatewayOpen
3. DCM derives service/response state on top of SGW diag seams
4. TEST_SCN consumes the diag path as verification evidence
end note

@enduml
